    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are entering a labyrinth of futuristic corridors that resemble a space station. Strangely, this place feels familiar...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/383f9473a7d8f07528f616e800ed0ddc.poster.avif?t=1759304096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/383f9473a7d8f07528f616e800ed0ddc.webm?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/383f9473a7d8f07528f616e800ed0ddc.mp4?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The corridors are filled with deadly laser traps and hostile robots patrolling the area. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/8b0a7f19ef7754d08b3431b612d0b161.poster.avif?t=1759304096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/8b0a7f19ef7754d08b3431b612d0b161.webm?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/8b0a7f19ef7754d08b3431b612d0b161.mp4?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use control panels to deactivate or activate traps, turning them into weapons against your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/50844b92d17b3b62314aab2eaf0c12e6.poster.avif?t=1759304096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/50844b92d17b3b62314aab2eaf0c12e6.webm?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/50844b92d17b3b62314aab2eaf0c12e6.mp4?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Along the way, explore lockers to find useful items such as Laser Cola for healing, weapons, and crucial notes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/f4b04d74c4d2c8a997215cb3d6aaaff1.poster.avif?t=1759304096\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/f4b04d74c4d2c8a997215cb3d6aaaff1.webm?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320310/extras/f4b04d74c4d2c8a997215cb3d6aaaff1.mp4?t=1759304096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware – a terrifying alien creature lurks in the corridors, waiting for the perfect moment to strike. Will you survive its wrath and escape this maze?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoid deadly laser traps</strong> that can kill you or unsuspecting enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight </strong> <strong>hostile robots</strong> with weapon and traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore and loot lockers</strong> for laser cola, and crucial notes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying alien creature </strong>that stalks you through the maze.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic graphics</strong> and <strong>minimal UI</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
